  <?dbhtml filename="fribidi.html"?>

  <title>FriBidi-&fribidi-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The FriBidi package is an implementation of the <ulink
      url="http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr9/">Unicode Bidirectional Algorithm
      (BIDI)</ulink>. This is useful for supporting Arabic and Hebrew alphabets
      in other packages.
    </para>

